{"tid":769403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[GDP] 搭客過少　韓國高鐵KTX仁川機場段最快今年9月正式廢止","createTime":"2018-08-06T06:56:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T07:18:59.000Z","uid":23707,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7453de65dc99c67a90ab7752c98838ef130411b9","tid":769403,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T06:56:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/216065/%E6%90%AD%E5%AE%A2%E9%81%8E%E5%B0%91-%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E9%AB%98%E9%90%B5ktx%E4%BB%81%E5%B7%9D%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E6%AE%B5%E6%9C%80%E5%BF%AB%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B49%E6%9C%88%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%BB%A2%E6%AD%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F216065%2F%25E6%2590%25AD%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%25B0%2591-%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2590%25B5ktx%25E4%25BB%2581%25E5%25B7%259D%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25B9%25B49%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25BC%258F%25E5%25BB%25A2%25E6%25AD%25A2&d=M0A8fxxVlwfyKGvn3oN%2BGTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=1c47fb31\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/216065/%E6%90%AD%E5%AE%A2%E9%81%8E%E5%B0%91-%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E9%AB%98%E9%90%B5ktx%E4%BB%81%E5%B7%9D%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E6%AE%B5%E6%9C%80%E5%BF%AB%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B49%E6%9C%88%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%BB%A2%E6%AD%A2</a><br />\n<br />\n今年3月仁川機場暫停了機場連接其他城市的KTX服務，韓國《中央日報》周五（27日）引述相關消息人士報道，國土部已在最近得出結論，將會完全廢止KTX仁川機場段，並會通知各地區政府協調。最快在今年9月實行。<br />\n<br />\nKTX連接首爾、大邱、釜山等主要大城市，KTX仁川機場段在2014年通車，但因長期乘客不足出現經營困難。根據KORAIL數字，仁川機場段平均搭客僅23%，全車八成座位空置。<br />\n<br />\n現時仁川機場已有機場鐵路直抵首爾，乘客若需搭乘KTX仍可在沿線的光明站或首爾站換乘。報道引述國土部指，相信廢止KTX不會對旅客造成太大影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"759286c29c138a7c3b5479a8e2117ecbe43cc86d","tid":769403,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T06:58:54.000Z","msg":"[wow] <br />\n貼乜鳩支港01 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dac83f5ee7cb150e6dfdf8d865f0177d1c73c76","tid":769403,"uid":23180,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T07:01:17.000Z","msg":"正常<br />\n<br />\n遲D香港果條無人搭<br />\n<br />\n就特登改到D交通工具駁去膠鐵迫香港人食番"},{"pid":"a552cb051202c11b9e27aaee9ffa980d5d797cad","tid":769403,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"759286c29c138a7c3b5479a8e2117ecbe43cc86d","tid":769403,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T06:58:54.000Z","msg":"[wow] <br />\n貼乜鳩支港01 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T07:03:29.000Z","msg":"咁邊份報紙最啱你睇？<br />\n<br />\n講下"},{"pid":"adbee99a8196d50fc8ed195e3a609b648c88aa4e","tid":769403,"uid":26602,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6dac83f5ee7cb150e6dfdf8d865f0177d1c73c76","tid":769403,"uid":23180,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T07:01:17.000Z","msg":"正常<br />\n<br />\n遲D香港果條無人搭<br />\n<br />\n就特登改到D交通工具駁去膠鐵迫香港人食番"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T07:07:37.000Z","msg":"大西北出尖沙咀三寶（260x 268b 269b）已經出左建議要兜一兜膠鐵站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b26ed07481bdd47211ec18c8a2724c01dd4f48","tid":769403,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T07:12:18.000Z","msg":"香港膠鐵都會步後塵"},{"pid":"cb0305fd7ab0f722841bf040fa075e9164a1db13","tid":769403,"uid":51720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T07:18:59.000Z","msg":"實情係：<br />\n仁川機場段原本只通機場鐵路（A'REX），係當局唔知點解要谷 KTX 便捷及客量，<br />\n「夾硬」將機場鐵路段月台「一分為二」。<br />\n（即係將部分高身月台，改建成方便 KTX 乘客上落嘅矮身月台）<br />\n參考網站：《繁忙的西船 Junction》 網站（<a href=\"http://www.2427junction.com/）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.2427junction.com%2F%EF%BC%89&d=M0A8fxxVlwfyKGvn3oN%2BGTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=5585ec4f\